ng\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5720:\"<p>We are happy to announce another addition with a new list of compatible themes, these are: <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/bazar-shop-multipurpose-ecommerce-theme/3895788\" target=\"_blank\">Bazar</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/room-09-shop-multipurpose-ecommerce-theme/4638247\" target=\"_blank\">Room 09</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/justshop-premium-beautiful-woocommerce-theme/4747148?ref=templatation\" target=\"_blank\">Justshop</a>, <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/themes/ifeature\" target=\"_blank\">iFeature</a> and <a href=\"http://www.gavick.com/wordpress-themes/rockwall,126.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rock Wall</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Themes \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Plugins \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and help you quickly make your theme <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Bazar theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/bazar-shop-multipurpose-ecommerce-theme/3895788\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-131966\" alt=\"bazarshop\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/bazarshop.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Bazar is a fresh and creative theme that utilises the WooCommerce plugin to create a WordPress powered shop with features such as wishlist, compare products and the zoom effect.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/bazar-shop-multipurpose-ecommerce-theme/3895788\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Bazar</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Room 09 theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/room-09-shop-multipurpose-ecommerce-theme/4638247\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-131968\" alt=\"room_09\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/room_09.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Room 09 is a clean and easy to customize WooCommerce theme. This theme includes a number of features such as wishlist, compare products and the product enquiry form (to use the theme like a catalog, without the cart).</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/room-09-shop-multipurpose-ecommerce-theme/4638247\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Room 09</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Justshop theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/justshop-premium-beautiful-woocommerce-theme/4747148?ref=templatation\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-131972\" alt=\"justshop\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/justshop.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>JustShop is modern, stylish WordPress theme template for Bakery items. JustShop is suitable for all desserts, cakes, food, pastry, bakery, sweets and other similar nature of business.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/justshop-premium-beautiful-woocommerce-theme/4747148?ref=templatation\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Justshop</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">iFeature theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/themes/ifeature\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-131970\" alt=\"ifeature\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/ifeature.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>iFeature 5 is responsive drag &amp; drop WordPress theme. It lets you create responsive website that you can control on any touch friendly device including the iPad, iPhone, and Android devices.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/themes/ifeature\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase iFeature</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Rock Wall theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.gavick.com/wordpress-themes/rockwall,126.html\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-131969\" alt=\"rockwall\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/rockwall.jpg\" width=\"593\" height=\"299\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>WordPress music theme designed for musicians, bands, artist, bloggers and the entertainment industry. Rock Wall theme is a good solution while building news and music websites. The theme is to rock, share and deliver the latest information from from the music world.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.gavick.com/wordpress-themes/rockwall,126.html\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Rock Wall</a></p>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:103:\"http://wpml.org/2013/06/this-week-compatible-bazar-room-09-justshop-ifeature-and-rock-wall-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"Now compatible – Principles, CoWorker, Minimal and Gommero\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"http://wpml.org/2013/05/now-compatible-principles-coworker-minimal-and-gommero/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"http://wpml.org/2013/05/now-compatible-principles-coworker-minimal-and-gommero/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 19 May 2013 09:14:40 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Compatibility Bulletin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"g