if you&#8217;re a theme  author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and help you quickly make your theme <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Principles theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://obox-design.com/theme.cfm/theme/principles\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128354\" alt=\"principles\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/principles.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Principles is simple, lightweight, box shaped, and mobile friendly WordPress Theme for bloggers and professionals. Create your own custom menu, you can also upload your own custom background and give your theme an individual touch.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://obox-design.com/theme.cfm/theme/principles\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Principles</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">CoWorker theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/coworker-responsive-retina-multipurpose-theme/4608484\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128350\" alt=\"coworker\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/coworker.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>CoWorker is a responsive theme built for flexibility. Be it a business, portfolio, agency or any other kind of website, CoWorker will work just fine for you. A good number of customizations are possible with this theme that&#8217;ll help you redefine your website&#8217;s brand value.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/coworker-responsive-retina-multipurpose-theme/4608484\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase CoWorker</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Minimal theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.obox-design.com//theme.cfm/theme/minimal\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128352\" alt=\"minimal\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/minimal.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>The Minimal theme is a content first minimalistic theme. It includes a distraction widget area which allows you to display an unlimited amount of different widgets, you can also use the Portfolio section in Minimal to show off some of your best work.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.obox-design.com//theme.cfm/theme/minimal\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Minimal</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Gommero theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.inkthemes.com/wp-themes/gommero-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128345\" alt=\"gommero\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/gommero.jpg\" width=\"570\" height=\"270\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Gommero is versatile and functional theme for everyone who has a website or blog. In the tradition of giving you something fresh, cool, technological, and fun WordPress theme &#8211; without compromising SEO and overall user experience.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.inkthemes