;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5666:\"<p>We are happy to announce another list of themes which are now compatible with WPML, these are: <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/mayashop-a-flexible-responsive-ecommerce-theme/2189918\" target=\"_blank\">Maya Shop</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/cheope-shop-flexible-ecommerce-theme/3409344\" target=\"_blank\">Cheope</a>, <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/suerte-corporate-portfolio-wp-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Suerte</a>, <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/samarcanda-fullscreen-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Samarcanda</a> and <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/stendhal-clean-portfolio-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Stendhal</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Themes \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Plugins \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins\" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin  <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Maya Shop theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/mayashop-a-flexible-responsive-ecommerce-theme/2189918\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-134892\" alt=\"maya\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/maya.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>MayaShop is a fresh WordPress theme that utilises the JigoShop and Woo Commerce plugins to create a versatile shop, with a good number layout options and skins.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/mayashop-a-flexible-responsive-ecommerce-theme/2189918\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Maya</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Cheope theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/cheope-shop-flexible-ecommerce-theme/3409344\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-134891\" alt=\"cheope\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/cheope.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Cheope is a clean and brandable theme. Some features of Cheope are: slider, zoom effect in the product detail page, popup plugin included to show offers and news and list/grid view in the products page.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/cheope-shop-flexible-ecommerce-theme/3409344\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Cheope</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Suerte theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/suerte-corporate-portfolio-wp-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-134893\" alt=\"suerte\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/suerte.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Suerte is a premium WordPress theme, built for your corporate/portfolio site or your personal blog. Suerte give a fresh and original perspective to your site.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/suerte-corporate-portfolio-wp-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Suerte</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Samarcanda theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/samarcanda-fullscreen-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-134894\" alt=\"samarcanda\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/samarcanda.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Samarcanda is a multipurpose WordPress theme that allow you to show your portfolio, images, videos with a fresh and creative perspective.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/samarcanda-fullscreen-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Samarcanda</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Stendhal theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/stendhal-clean-portfolio-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-134895\" alt=\"stendhal\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/stendhal.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Stendhal is a clean, usable corporate/portfolio theme. If you are looking for a easy to use/customize theme, with portfolio features and design options, Stendhal is a good choice for you.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/stendhal-clean-portfolio-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Stendhal</a></p>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\"