ank\">Di’verso</a>, <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/bolder-corporate-portfolio-wp-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Bolder</a>, <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/impero-minimalistic-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Impero</a>, <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/memento-a-flexible-corporate-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Memento</a>, <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/sheeva-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Sheeva</a>, <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/libra-corporate-portfolio-wp-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Libra</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/sommerce-shop-a-versatile-ecommerce-theme/542001\" target=\"_blank\">Sommerce</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Themes \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Plugins \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and help you quickly make your theme <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Pinkrio theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/pinkrio-responsive-multi-purpose-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133921\" alt=\"pinkrio1\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/pinkrio1.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>PinkRio is a theme with a clean and corporate layout. This theme is suitable for a corporate/brandable site and also for personal portfolio and blog. With the theme option panel and the shortcode manager you can customize the theme and create a different style.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/pinkrio-responsive-multi-purpose-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase PinkRio</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Di’verso theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/diverso-a-flexible-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133925\" alt=\"diverso1\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/diverso1.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Di’verso is a fresh and clean multipurpose theme, built for your corporate/portfolio site or your personal blog. Di’verso is easy to set and customize so you can create a different style for your needs.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/diverso-a-flexible-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Di’verso</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Bolder theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/bolder-corporate-portfolio-wp-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133916\" alt=\"bolder\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/bolder.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Bolder is a theme that is good for business, blogs, and portfolios among other things. It contains 15 different skins, 3 different sliders, 3 portfolio pages and a sleek nice design.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/bolder-corporate-portfolio-wp-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Bolder</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Impero theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/impero-minimalistic-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133927\" alt=\"impero\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/impero.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Impero is a minimalist theme, built for your corporate/portfolio site or your personal blog. With 5 different sliders and layout options, Impero is easy to set and customize.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/impero-minimalistic-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Impero</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Memento theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/memento-a-flexible-corporate-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133928\" alt=\"memento1\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/memento1.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Memento is a brandable and creative theme with a clean and corporate layout. You can create a different style and different sites with just one theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/memento-a-flexible-corporate-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Memento</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Sheeva theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/sheeva-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133929\" alt=\"sheeva1\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/sheeva1.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Sheeva is a simple theme with a clean layout. You can set any color to elements such as backgrounds, links, text and change the look of your site in few seconds. It includes a slider, 7 skins and and a good number of fonts.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/sheeva-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Sheeva</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Libra theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/libra-corporate-portfolio-wp-theme/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133923\" alt=\"libra\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/libra.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Libra is elegant looking clean WordPress theme. This theme is suitable for a brandable site and also for personal portfolio and blog. It comes with the theme options panel, so it&#8217;s easy to customize.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/libra-corporate-portfolio-wp-theme/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Libra</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Sommerce theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/sommerce-shop-a-versatile-ecommerce-theme/542001\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133914\" alt=\"sommerce\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/sommerce.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Sommerce theme utilises WooCommerce plugin to create a versatile WordPress shop, with a good number of layout options and skins.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/sommerce-shop-a-versatile-ecommerce-theme/542001\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Sommerce</a></p>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:108:\"http://wpml.org/2013/06/now-compatible-pinkrio-diverso-bolder-impero-memento-sheeva-libra-and-sommerce/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"This week compatible – Bazar, Room 09, Justshop, iFeature and Rock Wall themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"http://wpml.org/2013/06/this-week-compatible-bazar-room-09-justshop-ifeature-and-rock-wall-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:107:\"http://wpml.org/2013/06/this-week-compatible-bazar-room-09-justshop-ifeature-and-rock-wall-themes/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8: